.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, fuchsia, brown, orange, blood-red
There are 5 different nationalities: mexican, german, polish, british, american
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, havana, chaman, tiparillo, cain
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, 7up, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
5 different pets are kept: rat, goat, frog, turtle, ferret

1. the mexican is the person who likes aquamarine
2. the german is the owner of the rat
3. the person drinking juice is the person who likes fuchsia
4. the polish is the person drinking sprite
5. the person who likes fuchsia is to the right of the person who likes brown
6. the dannemann-smoker is the owner of the ferret
7. the havana-smoker is the person who likes orange
8. the person drinking 7up is in the middle
9. the british is on the far left
10. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the goat
11. the havana-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the turtle
12. the tiparillo-smoker is the person drinking hot-chocolate
13. the american is the cain-smoker
14. the british is to the left or right of the person who likes blood-red

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   british	|    polish	|     mexican	|    german	|    american	|
| Color		|    orange	|      blood-red	|      aquamarine	|     brown	|     fuchsia	|
| Beverage	|     soy-milk	|      sprite	|      7up	| hot-chocolate	|     juice	|
| Cigar		|     havana	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| tiparillo	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     goat	|     turtle	|     ferret	|     rat	|     frog	|
